### ============================================================
### SCHOOLS API - REST Client Testing
### ============================================================
### Base URL — sesuaikan jika port berbeda
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api

### ============================================================
### PRASYARAT DATA DUMMY
### Jalankan sekali jika belum ada data sekolah:
### php artisan migrate
### php artisan db:seed
### ============================================================

### ============================================================
### 1. LIST SEKOLAH (default — page 1)
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/schools
### ============================================================

# @name schoolListDefault
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/schools
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 2. LIST SEKOLAH - PAGINATION
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/schools?page=1&per_page=6
### ============================================================

# @name schoolListPagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/schools?page=1&per_page=6
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 3. SEARCH - by nama sekolah
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/schools?q=negeri
### ============================================================

# @name schoolSearchByName
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/schools?q=negeri
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 4. SEARCH - partial match (case insensitive)
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/schools?q=SMA
### ============================================================

# @name schoolSearchSMA
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/schools?q=SMA
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 5. DETAIL SEKOLAH
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/schools/{id}
### ID dari seeder: school.a (user id=8)
### Response termasuk: students, student_achievements, pengajuan_mitra
### ============================================================

@schoolId = 8

# @name schoolDetail
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/schools/{{schoolId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 6. DETAIL SEKOLAH - ID tidak ditemukan (404)
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/schools/999999
### ============================================================

# @name schoolDetailNotFound
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/schools/999999
Accept: application/json

###
